title: Etobicoke Creek station
text:
Etobicoke Creek is a <a href="bus%20rapid%20transit">bus rapid transit</a> station on the <a href="Mississauga%20Transitway">Mississauga Transitway</a> in <a href="Mississauga">Mississauga</a>, <a href="Ontario">Ontario</a>, Canada. It is located along the north side of <a href="Eglinton%20Avenue">Eglinton Avenue</a> at Tahoe Boulevard.
Tahoe and Etobicoke Creek opened on 16 February 2016.
